content: Titan-Node: Contributed two merged PRs this month, including a Twitter post formatting fix (#1070, removing 1,086 lines) and the addition of a Livepeer Image Provider (#1525, adding 475 lines). Activity was sporadic, occurring on just 2 days of the month, with contributions evenly split between code and documentation work. The PRs demonstrated a primary focus on feature development (63%) with some bugfix work (13%), taking an average of 6 hours to merge.
